Step-by-Step Execution in Exam
✅ STEP 1 — Create New Project

Open Android Studio → New Project
Select Empty Activity
Name: ImageSliderDemo
Package: com.example.imagesliderdemo
Language: Java
Min SDK: API 21
Click Finish → Wait for Gradle


✅ STEP 2 — Add Images to Drawable Folder ⭐ CRITICAL STEP

In left panel: app → res → drawable
Right-click drawable → Show in Explorer / Reveal in Finder
Copy-paste 4–5 image files into that folder
Name them: image1.jpg, image2.jpg, image3.jpg, image4.jpg, image5.jpg
Come back to Android Studio → It will auto-detect them
⚠️ Image names must be lowercase, no spaces, no special characters!


